         <notesStmt>
            
            <note rend="IDENTIFICATION">
               
               <p>Français 835, Bibliothéque national de France, Paris. Paris, ca. 1406-1408. </p>
            
            </note>
            
            <note rend="BASIC INFORMATION">
               
               <p>Parchment, 348 x 260 mm, 103 folios.</p>
            
            </note>
            
            <note rend="MATERIAL">
               
               <p>Ivory <material>parchment</material> with many humidity spots, some of them quite large, and with many unrepaired holes, seams and flies and two cuts. There are a few drops of wax in folios [<locus>56</locus>]v and [<locus>65</locus>]v. </p>
                             
            </note>
            
